This is a php image that is _based_ on

   https://github.com/million12/docker-nginx-php

but limits the installed software to the use of _running_ php / nginx / fpm.

# Usage

Make your document root

  /data/www/project/public

and run

  /config/bootstrap.sh

Nginx will be listening on port 8080

Changes to the original image:
- all output goes to stderr / stdout

removed software:
 - ruby
 - npm
 - gem
 - npm
 - gem
 - make
 - redis
 - mysql

added software:
 - php-memcache
 - php-memcached
